Package org.openmuc.jdlms.client.impl

Interface Summary
IAssociation  
ILowerLayerFactory Interface for sub layer factories used by ClientConnectionFactory
 

Class Summary
ClientConnectionFactory Actual implementation of ClientConnectionFactory.
Connection Base class used by all application level DLMS/Cosem connections
ConnectModule Small module shared by all ClientConnections that realizes the complete connection sequence between client and smart meter, authentication included Only a single connection can be tried to established (read as the act of connecting to the device) at a time.
DataConverter  
DisconnectModule Helper object that provides all Connection types with the same disconnection algorithm
HlsProcessorMd5 Implementation of the HIGH level authentication using MD5 as described in IEC 62056-62
HlsProcessorSha1 Implementation of HIGH Level authentication using SHA-1 hashing as described in IEC 62056-62
InterfaceClass Information about a single COSEM interface class needed by SNConnection
InterfaceClassList List of all supported COSEM interface classes
LNConnection Variant of the connection class using unencrypted messages with logical name referencing to communicate with the remote smart meter
ResponseQueue<E>  
SNConnection Variant of the connection class using unencrypted messages with short name referencing to communicate with the remote smart meter
